<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$huang-sen-jing" href="/people/huang-sen-jing">黄森婧</a>，<strong title="Web前端 In LiuZhou" class="zu-question-my-bio">Web前端 In LiuZhou</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="71">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ou-yang-xiao-liang-50" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ou-yang-xiao-liang-50" class="zg-link" title="晓梁">晓梁</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$shen-gun-zuo-zuo" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/shen-gun-zuo-zuo" class="zg-link" title="神棍那棍">神棍那棍</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ying-hua-fei-xue-zui-mei-shi-ni" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ying-hua-fei-xue-zui-mei-shi-ni" class="zg-link" title="相望不如相忘">相望不如相忘</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="962041" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">照这样说家境一般的大学生都不用谈恋爱了么。<br><br>大学的时候很多同学家里每个月父母都是给1000的生活费的。<br><br>稍微多点就是1500-2000<br><br>一个月看四场电影，周二半价，70两张，70乘以4=280，加8杯饮料。5*8=40.也就300来块。<br><br>学校里饭堂吃饭不贵，谁手快谁刷卡，也没有非要男朋友付款的理由。<br><br>偶尔一起泡泡图书馆，下晚自习散散步，就很满足了。<br><br>不要嫌弃这样的恋爱生活寒酸，我只能说，现在物质生活再好，从毕业后我再也找不到那样的感觉了。
<a href="/question/21953093/answer/19891404" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
